demo.name: ZW_ZnifferPTI_7_17_2_REGION_ANZ
demo.label: Z-Wave ZnifferPTI ANZ Region 7_17_2
demo.model:description:
Z-Wave ZnifferPTI ANZ Region 7_17_2
